282
00:40:58,956 --> 00:41:01,948
I didn't think so. Excuse me.

283
00:41:02,026 --> 00:41:05,325
All I know is,
the police are still investigating this one.

284
00:41:05,396 --> 00:41:06,693
That's why we still have the body.

285
00:41:06,764 --> 00:41:09,289
