00:55:11,641 --> 00:55:14,303
These recordings were used
in Terrence's trial.

431
00:55:17,614 --> 00:55:19,479
You'll see they speak for themselves.

432
00:55:23,787 --> 00:55:25,721
<i>Why did you set
