435
00:55:35,565 --> 00:55:40,059
<i>What made you think you absolutely
had to destroy those mirrors, Terrence?</i>

436
00:55:43,707 --> 00:55:48,644
<i>They killed my Helen
and my three children.</i>

437
00:55:49,412 --> 00:55:50,811
<i>For what reason?</i>

438
00:55:50,880 --> 00:55:52,279
<i>Why would mirrors
want to kill your family?</i>

439
00:55:52,349 --> 00:55:55,045
<i>- Because I didn't...
