440
00:55:57,487 --> 00:55:59,216
<i>They asked me to find Esseker.</i>

441
00:55:59,289 --> 00:56:00,313
Oh, my God.

442
00:56:00,390 --> 00:56:02,187
<i>We all are looking for Esseker.</i>

443
00:56:02,259 --> 00:56:03,954
Amy.

444
00:56:04,027 --> 00:56:06,086
Excuse me, I have to go.

445
00:56:07,430 --> 00:56:12,060
<i>Tell me about Esseker, Terrence.
